--VALUES--('8', '5.03973E+15', 'CGTNculture', '2024-5-30 13:44', "【洛阳桥介绍】洛阳桥，位于福建省泉州市洛阳江入海口，是中国第一座跨海石桥，被誉为“中国古代四大名桥之一”，建于北宋皇祐五年（1053年）。洛阳桥通过筏型基础和种蛎固基等独特工艺，成功解决了多个建桥难题。这座长达1200米的桥梁不仅展示了古代工匠的智慧，还见证了泉州作为“海上丝绸之路”重要港口的繁荣历史。洛阳桥的卓越设计和技术使其能够经受千年的风浪，至今仍屹立不倒。#洛阳桥 #泉州 #古代工程 #文化遗产 #桥梁建筑 Luoyang Bridge, located at the estuary of the Luoyang River in Quanzhou, Fujian province, is one of the &quot;Four Famous Ancient Bridges of China&quot;. Built in 1053 at the time of the Northern Song dynasty, it was China's first cross-sea stone bridge. Its construction employed a number of innovative techniques, such as raft foundations and oyster reef bases, to overcome the numerous challenges. At 1200 meters long, the bridge showcases the craftsmanship of the ancient builders and reflects Quanzhou's historical prominence as a key port on the Maritime Silk Road. Thanks to its exceptional design and technology, Luoyang Bridge has survived centuries of storms and remains standing to this day. #LuoyangBridge #Quanzhou #AncientEngineering #CulturalHeritage #BridgeConstruction #ExploreQuanzhou #QuanzhouHeritage #CGTN Inheritors", '0', '0', '1', '312', '141.1万', 'f', '', '北京', '北京', '中国')
